Got a, uh, another gold medal

04:24.600 --> 04:28.100
in the "broad" jump?

04:28.100 --> 04:31.200
You know,               
  you got a big mouth, Clavin.

04:31.200 --> 04:33.700
Hey, he happens                 
to be right, you know.

04:34.700 --> 04:36.900
Yeah, it's a genetic quirk      
in the, uh, Clavin family

04:37.000 --> 04:38.900
that we all have                
two extra teeth.

04:38.900 --> 04:40.200
Yeah, you see,

04:40.200 --> 04:41.800
that's the only way             
that we can prove

04:41.800 --> 04:46.000
that we are the rightful heirs  
to the Russian throne.

04:46.100 --> 04:49.800
Hello in there, Cliff.

04:49.800 --> 04:50.900
Tell me...

04:50.900 --> 04:54.400
what color is the 
              sky in your world?

04:56.000 --> 04:57.300
What's wrong?

04:57.400 --> 04:58.400
Carla, I just want to be left

04:58.500 --> 04:59.600
alone for a while, all right?

04:59.700 --> 05:01.300
You got it.                 
                  Thank you.

05:01.300 --> 05:04.100
Hey, everybody,                 
Sam wants to be left alone!

05:04.100 --> 05:06.300
Okay, Sammy,                    
spill your guts.

05:06.300 --> 05:07.500
What's the matter?

05:07.500 --> 05:09.300
Carla, I just said
