Yeah, but

05:09.300 --> 05:10.700
you're gonna end up             
telling me eventually,

05:10.700 --> 05:13.000
so you might as well            
get it over with.

05:13.000 --> 05:15.200
Go on,                          
make you feel better.

05:15.300 --> 05:16.700
Just keep this
