              show me something.

05:26.000 --> 05:27.400
What?

05:28.500 --> 05:30.000
My child.

05:30.000 --> 05:31.900
Seven pounds,   
                ten ounces,

05:31.900 --> 05:33.300
a baby boy.

05:34.100 --> 05:36.400
( <i>laughs</i> )

05:36.500 --> 05:40.100
( <i>laughing continues</i> )

05:40.100 --> 05:44.100
What's so funny?        
( <i>laughing continues</i> )

05:44.200 --> 05:46.000
Sam Malone finally got caught

05:46.000 --> 05:47.900
with his hand in the cookie jar.

05:47.900 --> 05:49.800
( <i>laughs</i> )

05:49.800 --> 05:50.300
Carla, come on.

05:50.400 --> 05:52.100
This is serious.

05:52.100 --> 05:54.500
Oh, of course it is, Sam.

05:56.000 --> 05:58.400
But I really think              
you're gonna be okay, you know?

05:58.400 --> 06:00.300
Yeah?         
Just remember this.

06:00.300 --> 06:02.600
