went to market...

06:02.600 --> 06:04.900
( <i>laughing</i> )

06:04.900 --> 06:06.300
Would you...?

06:06.400 --> 06:07.600
This is <i>not</i> funny.

06:07.600 --> 06:09.100
I'm sorry.

06:09.100 --> 06:10.400
You sure it's yours?

06:10.500 --> 06:13.200
No, it's between me       
        and another guy.

06:13.300 --> 06:14.500
But the kid's a real looker,

06:14.500 --> 06:16.700
so, you know,          
    you figure it out.

06:19.700 --> 06:21.900
So when are you         
      gonna find out, Dad?

06:21.900 --> 06:23.000
Soon.

06:23.100 --> 06:25.000
I mean, she dragged me down   
            to a lab

06:25.100 --> 06:27.100
to have a blood test.

06:27.100 --> 06:28.400
Well, what's                    
the big deal, you know?

06:28.400 --> 06:30.200
You can just do                 
what all the other jerks do.

06:30.200 --> 06:31.700
You pay a little money          
for support,

06:31.700 --> 06:33.000
and you get off the hook.

06:33.000 --> 06:34.700
No, Carla, it means a lot more 
        to me than that.

06:34.800 --> 06:37.900
