06:51.900 --> 06:53.600
Oh!

06:53.600 --> 06:56.100
I tell you, if I get      
  out of this, I swear to God,

06:56.100 --> 06:57.900
I am through fooling around   
            forever.

06:58.000 --> 06:59.900
Sam, don't swear to God.

06:59.900 --> 07:02.000
