I'll never have sex again.

07:05.800 --> 07:06.900
You?

07:06.900 --> 07:08.400
Never?

07:08.500 --> 07:09.000
Yeah, not ever.

07:09.000 --> 07:10.800
I mean, for the rest...

07:10.800 --> 07:14.100
Well, three months,       
         three months.

07:15.100 --> 07:17.800
Well, I guess the amount of sex 
    you have in three months

07:17.900 --> 07:20.500
is what most people       
      have in a lifetime.       
Huh.

07:20.500 --> 07:22.600
If they're attractive, I guess.

07:24.900 --> 07:26.400
You have a phone call      
          from Denise.

07:28.300 --> 07:30.200
