08:51.600 --> 08:53.800
Does the name "God"
             ring a bell?

08:53.800 --> 08:55.200
Yeah?

08:55.200 --> 08:57.100
The guy you         
            made a vow to?

08:57.100 --> 08:58.600
Oh.

08:58.700 --> 09:00.400
Yeah, boy, I almost             
forgot about that.

09:00.400 --> 09:02.700
Uh... it's no big thing.

09:02.700 --> 09:04.400
"No big thing"?

09:04.500 --> 09:06.300
Come on, God's a sport.

09:08.300 --> 09:09.800
People make promises            
like that all the time,

09:09.800 --> 09:11.800
