and more like Moses?

11:50.200 --> 11:52.300
Yeah, stop going      
          around scaring people.

11:52.300 --> 11:53.800
That's good.

11:53.800 --> 11:55.900
That's good,          
now, how 'bout the voice?

12:00.700 --> 12:03.300
Now sit down.

12:03.300 --> 12:04.800
Now...

12:04.900 --> 12:06.700
how can I be of help?

12:06.700 --> 12:09.800
Well, I would like          
      your advice, Father.

12:10.900 --> 12:13.900
Actually, it's for          
    a friend of mine.

12:14.000 --> 12:15.500
He, uh...

12:15.500 --> 12:18.000
got himself into kind of a bind,

12:18.000 --> 12:23.900
and so, in desperation, promised
  God he'd give up something.

12:23.900 --> 12:26.400
And what did he promise     
          to give up?

12:27.800 --> 12:29.400
Sweets.

12:30.400 --> 12:31.700
Oh.

12:31.700 --> 12:33.600
I see.             
          ( <i>chuckles</i> )

12:33.600 --> 12:35.700
Yeah...

12:35.700 --> 12:38.100
but my friend          
really likes sweets a lot.

12:39.800 --> 12:42.500
You know, and sweets      
        like him a lot.

12:42.500 --> 12:45.600
And he hasn't had sweets now  
      for about two weeks,

12:45.600 --> 12:48.800
